<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A0A1A7;--shiki-light-font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#7F848E;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic">// null</span></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="未定义值" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#未定义值"><span>未定义值</span></a></h3>
<p>未定义值 <code v-pre>undefined</code> 是全局对象的一个属性。也就是说，它是全局作用域的一个变量。<code v-pre>undefined</code> 的最初值就是原始数据类型 <code v-pre>undefined</code>。</p>
<div class="language-js line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="js" data-title="js" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34"><pre v-pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code"><code><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD">var</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#E06C75"> foo</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">;</span></span>
